TextEng: Is Lord Nasher well?
What needs to be done?
Farewell for now.
Spare me your lies. He is either deathly ill or dead.
Text: 헛소리는 집어치워. 그는 위독하든가 이미 죽었겠지.

TextEng: I suppose I am still restricted from entering the castle?
Tell Lord Nasher that I wish him a speedy recovery.
Text: 나셰르 영주님께 쾌유를 빈다고 전해 줘.

TextEng: I have another Waterdhavian creature. Do you want it?
Text: 워터딥의 생명체가 하나 더 있어. 원해?

TextEng: Nasher has shown no interest in me. He remains hidden.
Text: 나셰르 영주님은 내게 아무 관심도 보이지 않았어. 여전히 모습을 숨기고 계시지.

TextEng: Farewell, then.
Perhaps I could speak with Lord Nasher?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is Lord Nasher not well?
I found a Waterdhavian creature. Where should I take this?
Text: 워터딥의 생명체를 찾았어. 이걸 어디로 가져가야 해?

TextEng: Can you tell me anything about the plague?
Does he fear the plague so much?
I have just joined his service under Aribeth.
Text: 방금 아리베스 휘하에서 그의 명을 받들게 되었어.

TextEng: Me serve! Lemme in!
Scaredy-cat. Worry 'bout plague like baby.
Me need ask about sick.
Me find thingy! Water-whosian animal! Where does me take it?
Text: 나 거 찾았어! 워터-뭐시기 동물! 어디로 가져가?

TextEng: Me gots another Water-whosian animal! You want?
Text: 나 워터-뭐시기 동물 또 가져왔어! 너 원해?

TextEng: Me speak with Big Nasher?
Bah! Nasher no-show!
I go bye bye thens.
Give him wishes to gets better.
Now let me enter big castle?
He probably dead. You big liar.
What left to do?
Nasher still sick or better?
I goodbye now.
